      <div type="letter">
        <head>
          <title> 22 July / 2 August 1771. – Letter from the Russian chargé d’affaires in <persName
              key="p0363"
              ref="5ee062d0-b64c-4dd4-b0e9-f88cf7b05bda">Peter von Staehlin</persName>
          </title>
          <note>
            <bibl>AVPRI, fond 84, opis 2, no. 123, f. 14-14v. Ciphertext with French translation.</bibl>
          </note>
        </head>
        <pb n="f.14" />
        <p> Monseigneur </p>
        <p />
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2382.1117.1634.1969.1634.2781.1078.261.1479.672.846.431.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>Parmi les</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1956.2881.530.2397.1215.2666.455.1495.1445.1654.1426.1393.114.1735.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>projets d’Oeconomie</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1059.1176.1835.882.2104.2604.482.1012.1739.2346.1043.527.1176.1307.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>qui se font ici, pour</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1355.1908.2082.2604.1764.1634.1305.1021.1624.2774.1049.498.2070.2621.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>contribuer au retablissement </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2017.1921.1942.1619.1836.1244.2113.1392.848.1633.2572.2932.1376.80. </hi>
        </p>
        <p>des finances derangées de la Saxe, </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1313.1705.1716.2449.1738.857.2509.1821.456.1913.2902.2021.1290.971.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>il est question actuëlement d’une </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2193.1347.2038.714.1307.1664.1704.1048.650.1091.2702.2382.1871.1652.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>nouvelle reforme dans l’armée, qui doit</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">
            2499.1021.2593.2094.1763.1756.1283.1283.1210.1059.2410.1502.693.1291.1117.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>consister en 20. hommes par compagnie</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1967.1516.1043.1807.1835.899.1826.576.90.</hi>2459.1070.1908.885.1272.</p>
        <p>de façon que les Compagnies composées </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1630.2912.2169.1153.1004.924.1064.</hi>2886.1634.1321.1728.1987.1443.</p>
        <p>actuellement de 150 hommes ne le </p>
        <pb n="f.14v." />
        <p />
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1204.1942.1541.1091.1512.2171.483.2666.1716.2891.1208.2413.507.843.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>seroient à l’avenir, que 80. et surtout</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1605.1753.1664.456.2702.843.1642.1573.882.1461.2895.2146.</hi>2171.704.</p>
        <p>l’armée cela produiroit environ </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2443.1163.1773.1808.1064.1858.1993.2840.1156.885.</hi>1594.1634.2095.</p>
        <p>5/m hommes de diminues. </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2886.437.2176.1479.1870.2762.2987.1803.2780.1735.2431.1426.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>On pretend que par</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1043.2178.1890.1873.1807.2257.1797.2810.609.1135.2325.</hi>2922.1540.</p>
        <p>cette reforme la caisse</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2307.1893.1487.2182.2342.2205.2932.1025.1152.1152.1004.2254.1725.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>epargnera au dela de 300. mille Ecus</p>
        <p />
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">269.1244.2370.1987.1340.1029.1594.843.2098.710.2545.</hi>1444.778.</p>
        <p>par an pour le moins. Le Comte de </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1987.1406.23.1042.1509.592.1021.1740.1667.1395.1642.1799.1006.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>
          <persName key="p0866">Sacken</persName> est fort contraire à ce projet mais </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2868.1594.2886.1988.1614.1585.1807.1447.2900.1721.2164.2607.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>les autres ministres du</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2922.2714.1728.826.1206.2076.1942.688.1987.1912.2682.1885.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>Cabinet tachent de le faire gouter </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">2094.977.1091.2252.1387.1078.2556.1815.2655.2545.1285.1183.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>à <persName key="p0058" ref="db6f2ee9-5e05-41d1-86d9-15ea99f645d9">l’Electeur</persName>.
          Cependant </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1730.1244.1967.2051.1043.1093.2499.1615.1313.2205.1371.2017.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>on croit qu’il aura lieu, ce qui </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1874.2095.1078.1079.2914.1728.1180.1464.1049.423.2122.</hi>977.</p>
        <p>ne tardera pas à se</p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1908.2440.1213.2797.1346.2192.1457.1349.1467.2382.700.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>developper bientôt. </p>
        <p>
          <hi rendition="#s">1442.2382.1296.2231.1555.1445.1254.1895.2214.2987.15.1639.</hi>
        </p>
        <p>J’ai l’honneur d’etre avec le plus profond respect </p>
        <p> Monseigneur </p>
        <p> de Votre Èxcellence </p>
        <p />
        <p>
          <placeName key="g0013" ref="https://www.geonames.org/2935022">Dresde</placeName>
        </p>
        <p>Le 22. Juillet / 2. Août 1771</p>
        <p>le trés humble, trés obeiissant [sic],</p>
        <p>et trés soumis Serviteur </p>
        <p>
          <persName key="p0363" ref="5ee062d0-b64c-4dd4-b0e9-f88cf7b05bda">P. Stehlin</persName>
        </p>
      </div>
